OL,3,C'Unforgiveable': Report finds death of
OL,4,Clearning disabled man was preventable
OL,6,FThe inquest into the death of Myles
OL,7,FScriven in Huddersfield found multiple
OL,8,Fopportunities to save his life were
OL,9,Fmissed by staff at Calderdale Royal
OL,10,FHospital and his GP practice, after he
OL,11,Fdied from an entirely treatable blood
OL,12,Fclot in his leg.
