OL,6,FHe found healthcare professionals had
OL,7,Fa 'complacent and dismissive attitude
OL,8,Ftowards Myles and his learning
OL,9,Fdisability', clinicians were 'blind'
OL,10,Fto his needs, and did not make
OL,11,Fsufficient reasonable adjustments for
OL,12,Fhis disability.
