OL,6,F"It is unforgivable."
OL,8,F"It was trying to save their
OL,9,Freputation rather than reflecting and
OL,10,Ftrying to save peoples' lives with
OL,11,Flearning disabilities."
OL,13,FOfficial data shows that men with a
OL,14,Flearning disability die 20 years
OL,15,Fearlier than the general population in
OL,16,Fthe UK. Women with a learning
OL,17,Fdisability die on average 23 years
OL,18,Fyounger.
