OL,3,C'Unforgiveable': Report finds death of
OL,4,Clearning disabled man was preventable
OL,6,FProfessor Sara Ryan researches social
OL,7,Fcare with a specialism in learning
OL,8,Fdisabilities and autism. Her own son,
OL,9,FConnor Sparrowhawk, who was learning
OL,10,Fdisabled, autistic and had epilepsy,
OL,11,Fdied in 2013 whilst in the care of an
OL,12,FNHS assessment facility.
OL,14,F"I was struck by how similar Myles'
OL,15,Fdeath was to Connor's in that he died
OL,16,Fthrough the most woeful failings of
OL,17,Fhealthcare," she told ITV News.
OL,19,F"Connor was left to drown in a bath in
OL,20,Fa hospital unit, and he had diagnosed
OL,21,Fepilepsy."
