OL,6,F"We have to remember that people with
OL,7,Flearning disabilities aren't ill,"
OL,8,FProfessor Ryan said.
OL,10,F"There's no reason why people should
OL,11,Fbe dying so early. You have got a
OL,12,Ftsunami of evidence that says we know
OL,13,Fwhy people are dying, we know how
OL,14,Fpeople are dying, and we are doing
OL,15,Fnothing about it."
OL,17,FOutside Bradford Coroner's Court,
OL,18,FMyles' uncles reflected on the
OL,19,Fjudgement.
